    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A tough, flexible, transparent, moistureproof polyvinyl acetal resin made from polyvinyl alcohol and butyraldehyde; used, among other things, as the interlayer in safety glass and other laminated products.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000042061/Webster's Third New International Dictionary (1961)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Resina de polivinilo acetal y butiraldehído, dura, flexible, transparente e impermeable. Se utiliza entre otros en la capa intermedia de vidrios de seguridad y otros productos laminados.
</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Een taaie, soepele, transparante en vochtbestendige polyvinylacetaalhars gemaakt van polyvinylalcohol en butyraldehyde; wordt onder andere gebruikt als tussenlaag in veiligheidsglas en andere gelamineerde producten.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>一種質地堅韌、有彈性、透明、防潮的聚乙烯縮醛樹脂，由聚乙烯醛和丁醇製成。可加入其他成分製成安全玻璃和其他層壓產品的內層。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
